Package: SparseICA
Type: Package
Title: Sparse Independent Component Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2023-08-28
Author: Zihang Wang, Irina Gaynanova, Aleksandr Aravkin, Benjamin B. Risk
Maintainer: Zihang Wang <zihang.wang@emory.edu>
Description: A novel Sparse ICA method that enables sparse estimation of independent source components by solving a non-smooth non-convex optimization problem via the relax-and-split framework. The Sparse ICA balances statistical independence and sparsity simultaneously and is computationally fast.
